{"tid":1714896,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際記聯轟港警冇王管","createTime":"2019-11-13T03:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T03:27:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7faa53c144369c95343d326801890eb2941a6c38","tid":1714896,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191113/73NAEDEHHNBH2W3NAH6CENRBYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2F73NAEDEHHNBH2W3NAH6CENRBYY%2F&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE9wgLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=765c48a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2F73NAEDEHHNBH2W3NAH6CENRBYY%2F&h=0926ae8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191113/73NAEDEHHNBH2W3NAH6CENRBYY/</a><br />\n<br />\n國際記聯轟港警冇王管<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191113/large/1573576678_9521.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573576678_9521.gif&h=36c73965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIFJ成員Paul Murphy專程來港監察警察處理示威的手法。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國際記者聯盟（IFJ）成員、澳洲演藝人員工會（MEAA）主席Paul Murphy專程來港監察香港警察處理示威手法，來港聽取了多方講述香港自6月示威以來的情況。他認為，現存最大問題是沒有有效機制檢視警員不當行為，而他並不接受警方以電光火石之間作為攻擊記者的藉口。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：學生徵物資 一呼百應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不接受電光火石論<br />\n<br />\nPaul表示，過往較少留意香港局勢，但自今年6月起，澳洲傳媒多了許多關於香港示威的報道，令他留意到警方多次在示威現場向記者群方向發射催淚彈等攻擊，導致多名記者包括印尼女記者Veby Indah視力永久受損，認為記者在現場已穿上反光衣及有其他記認，不接受警方以電光火石之間作為攻擊記者的藉口（It's easy to tell who they are, there's no excuse for the police to target them for both physical or verbal assaults）。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，現時最大問題是沒有任何有效機檢視警方不當行為，正嚴重損害香港原有法治精神（There is no mechanism to review police's actions, that's a very serious breakdown of rule of law）。而北京政府背後支持警方，或是其中一個令警方繼續放肆的原因，他促請香港政府成立獨立調查警隊的機構，令涉事警員受到相關懲處，才可挽回公眾信心，否則香港只會走向專制社會，失去原有國際地位。<br />\n<br />\n另一名不願透露身份的國際專家指，周一看到有一名交通警員三度撞向示威者的影片，直斥不論放諸任何地方行為都是「nonsense」（荒謬）。她自己當日也身處彌敦道，看到私家車上有蒙面警員也感到十分害怕，因不知道他們何時會突然衝出來無預告地發動攻擊。她認為香港正處於關鍵時刻，明白港人多次透過和平手段得不到回應，但希望示威在網絡世代可更多元化及盡量保持和平。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王春怡"},{"pid":"62fea995d1d6b01ffde794f202cac379e2eeab71","tid":1714896,"uid":10737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:27:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4dfe9623b73bb95ee1dd4a116558b69d8506807","tid":1714896,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"出門之前 rt like reply<br />\n<br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙:bangbang::bangbang:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE9wgLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=e4e9dfb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Menendez 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE9wgLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=6cf6927e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&h=6fdcee86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Cotton 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sentomcotton/status/1194354865432092673?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsentomcotton%2Fstatus%2F1194354865432092673